        "id": "c010",
        "text": "3.\nConfidential Information shall not include information that Recipient can demonstrate by competent written proof is now, or hereafter\nbecomes, through no breach of this Agreement by Recipient, generally known or available or is hereafter furnished to Recipient by a third\nparty, as a matter of right and without restriction on disclosure.",
